cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques to infer 3D representations of objects from single images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and rendering techniques, which could fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The use of convolutional networks suggests a focus on deep learning, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with the transformation of point clouds into surface meshes, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics and Control).
